{"tid":1586841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【玩死TVB】門路原來係騙局！齊俾一星安信兄弟","createTime":"2019-09-22T07:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:13:48.000Z","uid":113630,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"983dde1b5b8a1d118711369f9d11b09993a2e578","tid":1586841,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"😈【新一波玩死TVB行動 - WeWa剪卡挑戰升級行動】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCtTLu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCtTLu3.png&h=e59223a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得今年年頭有個&ldquo;門路&rdquo;app喺CCTVB大賣廣告？搵杜汶澤出嚟講創業，仲話可以幫你搵資金💰。佢哋仲會搵TVB奀星主持創業訪談節目。唔好以為呢個app可以幫你聯絡初創基金呀⚠！<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">其實成件事都係安信兄弟為一眾有創業夢年青人搞嘅一個局</span></strong></span>，目的係sell後生仔借錢搞生意。創業未必次次都成功，如果最後失敗嘅話冇錢還會有咩下場，自己諗喇！拖糧唔單只會俾人告，仲可能會俾公審。借錢唔還可能連屋企都冇得返，小心中伏呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完呢篇文就更了解門路嘅真面目！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.kontent.com.hk/app/sectionDetail/429590905616334848?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.kontent.com.hk%2Fapp%2FsectionDetail%2F429590905616334848%3F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=86a748e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.kontent.com.hk/app/sectionDetail/429590905616334848?</a><br />\n<br />\n由於安信唔肯喺9月20號中午回應撤回TVB廣告嘅訴求，WeWa挑戰要再升級😠⬆！<br />\n<br />\n下載&ldquo;門路&rdquo;、&ldquo;安信兄弟&rdquo;及&ldquo;OmyCard&rdquo;app，再喺App Store或Google Play俾一星，然後留言，話&ldquo;呃人借錢兼資助TVB假新聞，安信契弟出賣港人，呼籲抵制到底！&rdquo;。當然俾完一星就刪咗個app佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然要去&ldquo;門路&rdquo;個專頁派嬲，再用呢幅圖留言洗板啦！傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Munroadshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMunroadshk%2F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=90f1fdbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Munroadshk/</a><br />\n<br />\n直至安信回應以下訴求為止：<br />\n1⃣宣佈撤回TVB廣告<br />\n2⃣停止使用TVB藝人主持門路節目<br />\n另外兩個訴求以及回應死線容後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊三日，抵制TVB行動仲會爆出更多安信嘅黑幕同埋對付安信嘅升級行動，千祈唔好錯過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">記住，財務公司係TVB第二大廣告客戶，安信係大客嚟架！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n資料來源：TVB認客戶押後廣告 稱無重大影響 網民籲商戶停光顧 無綫：報道公正不偏 明報 2019年7月11日&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1562785547117&amp;issue=20190711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1562785547117%26issue%3D20190711&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=6c1094c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1562785547117&amp;issue=20190711</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n🏃🏻&zwj;♂️👉請即follow:FB:&nbsp;#sayno2tvb&nbsp;or 五毛電視cctvb - 廣告宣傳部<br />\nIG: #sayno2tvbTG <br />\n抵制廣告行動組:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvbTG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvbTG&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c289d378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvbTG</a> <br />\n狙擊綜合頻道:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=a046586b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a>"},{"pid":"e13f65aa44506504644baf0041d0d97d22ea20aa","tid":1586841,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"